node.text: Hi, going anywhere today??!? Haha 😂 Just asking for the sake of it! Gotta keep the dreams alive! 👍🏻 Dreams of freedom, play dates, catching up with frens over a cuppa ☕️, swimming 🏖 & so much more... ♥️
Dress up at home is fun too!
😂 Going home 🏡  Soon cutie, I hope! 🤞
Meow’s home Gracey !! Happy Bonding Day 🐈❤️🐶🐾:))
Can’t wait to play again soon jiejie! 😁
We hope the CB measures will be eased soon! 🤞🏼
Aww, you look so amazing staying safe at home my beautiful furiend🥰♥️😘
Awww so pretty ❤️❤️ love your dress up 😘😘
